keys.string: Hey, man, how’s it going? Learn anything new on your first day?
I mean, I learned not to forget my syllabus.
Yeah, cloud computing’s pretty popular. But not as popular as Amini’s hair.
I walk away, too uncomfortable to respond.
Oh, baby, into that VR craze? I think it’ll teach us some interesting virtual...
Machine learning. I could think of some things to teach a computer.

ArrayOfString.string: [Seth][Dialog]Hey, man, how’s it going? Learn anything new on your first day?
[Player][Dialog]I mean, I learned not to forget my syllabus.
[Seth][Option]On the first day? That sucks. As long as you don’t forget the homework. The teachers wouldn’t like that one bit. Thinking of anybody as your mentor yet?
[Seth][Dialog]Yeah, cloud computing’s pretty popular. But not as popular as Amini’s hair.
[Narrator][Dialog]I walk away, too uncomfortable to respond.
[Seth][Dialog]Oh, baby, into that VR craze? I think it’ll teach us some interesting virtual...
[Seth][Dialog]Machine learning. I could think of some things to teach a computer.
